&ANALYZE-SUSPEND _UIB-CODE-BLOCK _PROCEDURE OCX.HTTPServerConnection Procedure 
PROCEDURE OCX.HTTPServerConnection :
/*------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  Purpose:     
  Parameters:  <none>
  Notes:       
------------------------------------------------------------------------------*/
  Run GetData ("webutil/_sdoinfo.p",
                "?function="     + xFunction
                + "&procedure="  + pProc
                + "&Columns="    + pCols
                + "&Properties=" + pProps ).
END PROCEDURE.

